title: BHAA - race starts for 2007
name: BHAA - race starts for 2007
description:
A Map by Bhaa

This map shows the locations of races organised by the Business Houses Athletic Association during 2007.

Registration is usually at a local sports club or school with the race starts close by.  

More details of races and information on the BHAA can be found at www.bhaa.net.
